4
00:02:12,199 --> 00:02:13,770
It's probably because...

5
00:02:15,069 --> 00:02:17,080
I said something at the class meeting.

6
00:02:17,210 --> 00:02:18,080
What did you say?

7
00:02:21,810 --> 00:02:23,110
I said...

8
00:02:24,550 --> 00:02:25,680
I didn't like women.

9
00:02:25,750 --> 00:02:26,550
