11
00:02:30,020 --> 00:02:31,490
It was a slip of the tongue.

12
00:02:34,159 --> 00:02:35,289
I see.

13
00:02:38,500 --> 00:02:39,430
No wonder...

14
00:02:40,729 --> 00:02:43,430
some guys have been asking about you.

15
00:02:44,439 --> 00:02:45,840
Back then,

16
00:02:46,270 --> 00:02:48,710
I thought you offended their girlfriends.

17
00:02:52,139 --> 00:02:54,210
From now on, just cover for me.

18
00:02:55,680 --> 00:02:56,879
Just tell them...

19
00:02:57,550 --> 00:02:58,650
