22
00:03:05,689 --> 00:03:06,719
I'm telling you.

23
00:03:06,960 --> 00:03:10,159
I'm a straight guy.

24
00:03:10,360 --> 00:03:11,599
I'm not interested in you.

25
00:03:11,659 --> 00:03:12,729
Don't forget about Yun Sheng.

26
00:03:13,129 --> 00:03:14,699
