37
00:03:43,030 --> 00:03:44,530
If you don't go, the consequences will be serious.

38
00:03:44,599 --> 00:03:45,330
Yes.

39
00:03:48,629 --> 00:03:49,599
What consequences?

40
00:03:52,300 --> 00:03:53,069
Tell him.

41
00:03:57,939 --> 00:04:00,280
When you talk to your girlfriend on the phone,

42
00:04:00,409 --> 00:04:01,449
I will sit next to you...

43
