and call your name in a feminine voice.

44
00:04:03,650 --> 00:04:05,780
"Hello, Bai Bai."

45
00:04:05,849 --> 00:04:07,889
"Who are you calling?"

46
00:04:07,949 --> 00:04:09,719
"Why are you ignoring me?"

47
00:04:09,789 --> 00:04:11,460
