52
00:04:29,509 --> 00:04:31,009
Don't just drink.

53
00:04:31,180 --> 00:04:32,040
Say something.

54
00:04:33,509 --> 00:04:34,610
About what?

55
00:04:36,009 --> 00:04:38,250
What's with you and Ms. Kang?

56
00:04:42,250 --> 00:04:43,660
What did she tell you?

57
00:04:52,230 --> 00:04:53,199
She said...

58
00:04:55,629 --> 00:04:57,199
that she felt bad for you.

59
00:04:58,839 --> 00:05:00,370
She wanted to see you again...

60
00:05:01,139 --> 00:05:02,209
and talk to you.

61
00:05:02,670 --> 00:05:03,839
What's there to talk about?

62
00:05:05,279 --> 00:05:06,279
I understand.

63
00:05:07,480 --> 00:05:09,579
I shouldn't hate her given the circumstances.

64
00:05:12,519 --> 00:05:13,920
But if it weren't for her,

65
00:05:14,319 --> 00:05:16,649
my family wouldn't have become like this.

66
00:05:17,560 --> 00:05:18,759
My hometown...

67
00:05:18,990 --> 00:05:20,089
