68
00:05:20,660 --> 00:05:22,990
Everyone knows about my dad's affair.

69
00:05:24,660 --> 00:05:25,829
He ruined my family.

70
00:05:27,069 --> 00:05:28,170
He was addicted to gambling.

71
00:05:29,199 --> 00:05:31,100
He angered his dad and wife to death.

72
00:05:32,600 --> 00:05:35,040
I'm here at the Art Institute to study design...

73
00:05:35,439 --> 00:05:38,180
to rebuild my family's jewelry store.

74
00:05:39,379 --> 00:05:41,680
I want to redeem our ancestral house...

75
00:05:46,220 --> 00:05:48,149
so that my mom can rest in peace.

76
00:05:49,550 --> 00:05:52,959
Every family has problems.

77
00:05:53,620 --> 00:05:55,990
Your family is indeed having a hard time.

78
00:05:56,889 --> 00:05:59,459
My family is on easy mode.

79
00:05:59,730 --> 00:06:02,769
Your family is on harder than hard mode.

80
00:06:04,740 --> 00:06:06,269
Things are not easy for my family either.

81
00:06:06,339 --> 00:06:07,410
What happened to your family?

82
00:06:17,050 --> 00:06:17,879
My mom...

83
00:06:22,050 --> 00:06:23,290
My mom passed away earlier this year.

84
00:06:30,360 --> 00:06:31,600
Things are really tough...

85
00:06:33,329 --> 00:06:34,829
