86
00:06:40,069 --> 00:06:41,439
Everyone in this world...

87
00:06:41,839 --> 00:06:43,269
has a scar.

88
00:06:44,009 --> 00:06:46,480
If we are held back by the past,

89
00:06:46,810 --> 00:06:48,310
how do we give a bright future...

90
00:06:49,180 --> 00:06:50,550
to those we care about?

91
00:06:51,519 --> 00:06:52,220
That's right.

92
00:06:55,649 --> 00:06:56,449
Come on.

93
00:06:59,220 --> 00:07:00,259
Let's...

94
00:07:00,990 --> 00:07:01,990
drink...

95
00:07:02,290 --> 00:07:03,629
to our unhappy past.

96
00:07:04,000 --> 00:07:05,230
- Cheers. - Cheers.

97
00:07:08,230 --> 00:07:09,329
If you're doing this...

98
00:07:09,670 --> 00:07:11,069
for the past,

99
00:07:11,339 --> 00:07:12,569
